			<element kind="staticText" uuid="432d04f2-f3ad-40ef-99c5-6137a70e06b6" x="-2" y="260" width="550" height="80">
				<text><![CDATA[Analysis:
The bar chart illustrates the total consumption of different feed types across the farm. 
The results show that certain feed types, such as corn and mixed feed, have higher usage 
compared to others. This indicates their importance in the farm’s nutrition plan and 
highlights patterns in feeding strategies.
]]></text>
			</element>
			<element kind="staticText" uuid="7106076f-1445-4161-b138-49ac29575a91" x="-2" y="350" width="551" height="90">
				<text><![CDATA[Conclusion:
This report provided an overview of feed usage efficiency in the farm management system.
The analysis helps in understanding feeding patterns and supports better decision-making
for optimizing nutrition and resource utilization in the farm.
]]></text>
